---
const bars = Array.from({ length: 48 }, (_, index) => 22 + ((index * 17) % 62));
---

<div class="editor-mock" aria-label="如是我闻编辑器界面示意">
  <div class="editor-mock-bar">
    <div class="editor-mock-dots" aria-hidden="true">
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
    </div>
    <span class="editor-mock-file">lecture_01_raw_audio.wav</span>
    <span class="editor-mock-spacer" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </div>

  <div class="editor-mock-wave">
    <div class="editor-mock-playhead" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="editor-mock-bars" aria-hidden="true">
      {bars.map((height) => <span style={`height: ${height}%`}></span>)}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="editor-mock-segments">
    <article class="editor-segment">
      <time>00:01:23</time>
      <p>同学们好，我们今天这节课主要讲一下中国古代文学批评史里的几个核心概念。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="editor-segment is-active">
      <time>00:01:45</time>
      <p>特别是“意象”这个词，它不仅仅是一个文学术语，更涉及到一种独特的哲学认知方式。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="editor-segment is-dim">
      <time>00:02:10</time>
      <p>大家可以翻开教材的第三十四页，看那段关于《文心雕龙》的引述。</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>
